 GHz. Conclusions: Together with the recent non-detection of W0855 at 4-8\nGHz, our constraints on the steady and pulsed emission from W0855 confirm that\nthe object is neither radio-loud nor magnetospherically particularly active.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2020 13:02:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
